com.dhemery.victor

Class Shelley

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dhemery.victor.IosViewIdentifier
      • com.dhemery.victor.Shelley

  • public class Shelley
extends IosViewIdentifier
    Identifies views using a Shelley pattern. For Frank to find views using Shelley identifiers, the Shelley selector engine must be running in the Frankified iOS application and registered with Frank under the name "shelley_compat". If the libShelley.a library is linked into the application, Shelley runs in the application, registered under the required name.
